Najipa subira siwalisema jiko lina toka kwa mungu ila najikuta mpweke Berna eti penzi nalo lina pana elimu  

maumivu ya yangu ninani 
Atakaye kuja kuya ponya 
Lichozi la jicho langu ninani atakaye kuja kulifuta 
 Popote ulipo juwa nakama bado nakutafuta 

Jamani 
Ivi muhulize kama iko jiyani?
Ivi niambiye anawa kina nani?

Uje kwangu uwe upepo mi nika enjoy uwepowako ela nitafute kwabidi na mimi ni fahamu samani yako na usije kubadili  na usilifanye penzi langu kuwa lakiki 
